{"tid":2015573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急]有冇人琴晚(13/5)係錦上路附近執到銀包","createTime":"2020-05-13T19:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T19:22:49.000Z","uid":320593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"39382b8ec8b10b5e89b977c4f0cd362f6829edd3","tid":2015573,"uid":320593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T19:01:13.000Z","msg":"代朋友po<br />\n13/5 夜晚十一點半至十一點四十五分 係錦上路西鐵站附近唔見咗銀包<br />\n銀包係手造啡色皮 白色線<br />\n入面有 $1000現金 (兩張500)<br />\n有身分證 回鄉証 安全咭 工人註冊証 Visa卡 Tap&amp;go卡 渣打銀行卡 仲有學生證 <br />\n錢冇咗唔緊要 冇證返唔到工 整返要好耐 好影響生計 想搵返<br />\n真係好重要<br />\n希望有人執到 可以俾返佢<br />\n麻煩大家幫幫手<br />\n唔該晒"},{"pid":"1584dc208469b1ba3a9a03e73c0e87ec8704c375","tid":2015573,"uid":320593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T19:01:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9d1af4448f5f8f78d983b631846ae112dbda88","tid":2015573,"uid":320593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T19:01:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6073aa3a64b129fa7501af3fed70cdae9a9e3ee0","tid":2015573,"uid":320593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T19:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d7ceb516876fdb652b563d9d448136716bb656","tid":2015573,"uid":320593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T19:22:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d64c21674fac069f056436cbfc17fde88f3d7cf0","tid":2015573,"uid":320593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T19:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}